### Day 6: create a coding conversation and store its id for following requests
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java debugging session"
}

> {% client.global.set("codingConversationId", response.body.id); %}

### Day 6: send a message in the created conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请帮我分析这段 Java 代码的 bug",
  "conversationId": "{{codingConversationId}}"
}

### Day 6: inspect the stored user message, answer, and route metadata
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/{{codingConversationId}}/messages

### Day 6: list all conversations ordered by latest activity
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations

### Day 6: create an isolated daily-planning conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Daily planning test"
}

> {% client.global.set("dailyConversationId", response.body.id); %}

### Day 6: first daily request, constrained to one sentence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请用一句话为我制定明天上午的学习计划。",
  "conversationId": "{{dailyConversationId}}"
}

### Day 6: follow up in the same conversation, also constrained to one sentence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请用一句话总结上面的讨论。",
  "conversationId": "{{dailyConversationId}}"
}

### Day 6: verify that the daily conversation contains four messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/{{dailyConversationId}}/messages


